  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the air fryer to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Cut the carrots, zucchini, red bell pepper, and onion into bite-sized pieces.",
    "Peel the ginger and cut it into thin slices.",
    "In a large bowl, mix together the cumin, paprika, powdered sugar, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the vegetable oil to the bowl and toss to coat the vegetables evenly.",
    "Spread the vegetables in a single layer in the air fryer basket.",
    "Cook for 10 minutes, shaking the basket halfway through.",
    "Add the ginger slices to the air fryer basket and continue cooking for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in the lemon juice and fresh parsley and mint.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional parsley and mint if desired."
  ],
